{"tid":742961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7分鐘急降8000米  數十乘客耳鼻噴血","createTime":"2018-07-15T04:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T03:26:08.000Z","uid":28366,"like":93,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"cab9081f8079bdc3f307afe57de0ff633869bf37","tid":742961,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/125113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F125113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=954bd271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廉航瑞安航空(Ryanair)周五一班由都柏林飛往克羅地亞的客機，因為機艙失壓，7分鐘內急降近8000米(26000呎)，數十名乘客耳鼻出血，幸好客機最後安全降落德國法蘭克福機場，33名乘客需要送院。<br />\n<br />\n一名需要送院的21歲乘客說，客機在約5分鐘內急速下降，「我的耳朵像要爆炸一般」。他說，雖然感到痛楚，但飛機降落後，仍要在機艙內等了20分鐘才獲得治療，最後證實耳膜沒有破裂，但耳膜後積了大量液體，主要是血液，需要多日才消散，在此期間要食止痛藥，並且不能乘坐飛機。 另一名乘客則表示客機「在少於一分鐘內下降3000米」，機艙內的氧氣罩都掉下，不少人感到耳痛，但他讚揚機師表現出色。<br />\n<br />\n瑞安航空發言人證實一班航機因機艙失壓需轉飛法蘭克福，機員根據正常程序，放下機艙氧氣罩及啟動可控制下降程序，作為預防措施，小量乘客接受了治療。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/125122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F125122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4567c9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最後安全降落</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180715/58443764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180715%2F58443764&d=NfhGcV7ouBHz7GOcl1%2FIvL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8bb1edee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180715%2F58443764&h=eaf2214c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180715/58443764</a>"},{"pid":"2060ebc87