br />\n就好似係飛機嘅薯片脹晒氣咁<br />\n<br />\n至於急降係相當合理<br />\n每分鐘跌3千幾尺唔係受傷主因<br />\n<br />\n利申業餘飛機撚 留名等專業人士指導小弟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"即係記者又誤導人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明急降係救命，寫到好似急降搞到乘客受傷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"擺明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有邊單飛機新聞唔係九宵驚魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d365a71cda18626823a60ba2d22e48a983113b","tid":742961,"uid":35199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf47c67b3d895d5fb882feef2239ee4e3fe74b4d","tid":742961,"uid":14346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"地面氣壓高過高空氣壓<br />\n飛機有氣泵&amp;氣閘控制住客艙嘅氣壓喺接近地表嘅水平<br />\n防止人體腔內壓同出邊氣壓差太遠而細胞爆裂/爆血管<br />\n同時高空嘅低氣壓意味空氣稀薄，人會缺氧<br />\n突然失壓通常係個客艙穿窿漏氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"唔駛氣泵， 高壓氣由引擎壓縮機部份提供。"},{"pid":"33ece99f0c5be7b6e7808a3baa6e56297407806f","tid":742961,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"睇過套戲啲人就係咁死曬<br />\n但佢地唔知自己死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26835a8a8624a4c04291847d3ccebb4526547b07","tid":742961,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T15:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a5b6895a9707e705b47de95421c18361981480","tid":742961,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T00:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9e67cf452843583c05a034f116a541bfeb3de4","tid":742961,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T00:13:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9148ac720c3312fec2028b22e154a4ac60b3c32c","tid":742961,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T01:29:36.000Z","msg":"ryanair<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過堅平 幾歐就有張單程"},{"pid":"ebbbbd12a0c3e4d60792e06ec1c51cab624e9086","tid":742961,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T01:41:58.000Z","msg":"中國國航客機萬米驚悚急降 引發安全與特權的網絡爭議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-44811863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-44811863&d=NfhGcV7ouBHz7GOcl1%2FIvL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7c5ad124\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-44811863&h=d832a1e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-44811863</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>「從11000米降到了4000米」<br />\n7月10日，CA106航班原計劃於17：55從香港機場出發，後起飛時間延誤至19：11，並於22：29到達大連。<br />\n<br />\n有機上乘客向中國媒體《新京報》表示，在19點50分左右，飛機先後兩次廣播「機艙失密」，下放緊急面罩，同時機艙溫度升高，「空調系統都沒有了」，「非常害怕」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另一位乘客的手機GPS顯示，當時飛機的飛行高度「從11000米降到了4000米左右」。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n中國國航客機冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb7a99bf140c90308a4b05361f77647690c5c9f","tid":742961,"uid":71703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T01:51:52.000Z","msg":"咁樣急降既話 離心力咪大到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c17cff4a33030a0476b8ca651887c0b8691fdc","tid":742961,"uid":80416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"乜撚野標題係度誤導人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6bba6176d4eca31bcc3c2cbd0c06b550c69464","tid":742961,"uid":150510,"like":0,"dislik